    if(score<=2):

    elif(score==3):
        return "neutral"
    else:
        return "positive"

def get_result(statement):
    result = model.predict([statement])
    pos = np.where(result[1][0] == np.amax(result[1][0]))
    pos = int(pos[0])
    sentiment_dict = {0:'negative',1:'neutral',2:'positive'}
    print(sentiment_dict[pos])
    return
